How do I buy North Atlantic Smaller Cos Inv Tr PLC stock? 

Shares of North Atlantic Smaller Cos Inv Tr PLC and other U.K. stocks can be purchased through online brokerage accounts that support trading on the London Stock Exchange (LSX). Some U.K. companies can be purchased through major U.S. brokerages in the form of American Depository Receipts (ADRs), which are placeholder equities held in a trust by a bank that represent shares of a foreign stock.



