Frequently Asked Questions for Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC (LON:EKF)
What is Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC's stock symbol?

Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC trades on the London Stock Exchange (LON) under the ticker symbol "EKF."



When will Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC make its next earnings announcement?

Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC is scheduled to release their next quarterly earnings announcement on Monday, September, 11th 2017. View Earnings Estimates for Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC.



Where is Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC's stock going? Where will Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC's stock price be in 2017?

1 analysts have issued 12 month price targets for Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC's stock. Their predictions range from GBX 19 to GBX 21. On average, they anticipate Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC's stock price to reach GBX 20 in the next twelve months. View Analyst Ratings for Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC.



Who are some of Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC's key competitors?

 Some companies that are related to Ekf Diagnostics Holding PLC include ConforMIS (CFMS), Zymeworks (ZYME), Mereo BioPharma Group PLC (MPH), Faron Pharmaceuticals Oy (FARN), Spring Bank Pharmaceuticals (SBPH), Allergy Therapeutics plc (AGY), Asterias Biotherapeutics (AST), Asterias Biotherapeutics (AST), Merus Labs International (MSLI), Synthetic Biologics (SYN), Kadmon Holdings (KDMN), Sinclair Pharma PLC (SPH), Chromadex Corp (CDXC), Nobilis Health Corp (HLTH), OncoCyte Corp (OCX), Matinas BioPharma Holdings (MTNB), Summit Therapeutics PLC (SUMM) and Pfenex (PFNX).



